  "title": "The `insightsClient` option has not been provided to `instantsearch`",
  "body": "When I click anywhere on my search result it show a error on console \r\n\r\n**The `insightsClient` option has not been provided to `instantsearch`** \r\n\r\nThe same in your netlify example as well - https://instantsearchjs.netlify.com/examples/e-commerce/search/?query=books\r\n\r\n**Steps to reproduce**\r\n1. Search anything\r\n2. Click on the search result items\r\n\r\nHow can I fix this? \r\n\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6106479/71242584-46b8a900-2334-11ea-9fbe-385625243d03.png)\r\n",
